    <div class="pageheader">
        <div class="headercontent">
            <div class="section-container">                               
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <p>I am a First year PhD student at Computer Science Department of  Aalto University, Finland.</p>
			<p>My supervisor is <a href=https://users.ics.aalto.fi/praiko/>Tapani Raiko</a>.</p>                           
                        <p>My research interest primarily lies in designing efficient optimization algorithms for Deep Architectures. To this end, I am working on the ideas based on transforming the outputs of hidden neurons of the networks. Tranformation based approaches have been shown to be very effective previously. Example of these approaches include <a href=http://jmlr.csail.mit.edu/proceedings/papers/v22/raiko12/raiko12.pdf>Deep learning made easier by linear transformations in perceptrons</a>, <a href=http://arxiv.org/abs/1502.03167>Batch Normalization: Accelerating Deep Network Training by Reducing Internal Covariate Shift</a>, <a href=https://papers.nips.cc/paper/5953-natural-neural-networks.pdf>Natural neural networks. </a> </p>   
   			<p>Application area wise, my research interest primarily lies in computer vision and natural language processing.</p>                      
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="subtitle text-center">
                            <h3>Research Interests</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="ul-boxed list-unstyled">
                            <li>Optimization algorithms for Deep Architectures</li>
                            <li>Non-convex optimization</li>
			    <li>Structured prediction</li>
                            
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>                
            </div>        
